|--------|---------|
| `npm run start` | Standard dev server (port 8081) |
| `npm run start:worktree` | Worktree-safe (port 8082, auto-clear cache) |
| `npm run versions` | Print all key package versions |
| `npm run doctor` | Run expo-doctor validation |
| `npm run validate` | Full validation pipeline |

## Upgrade Script
`scripts/upgrade-expo.sh` — Reusable SDK upgrade tool.
```bash
./scripts/upgrade-expo.sh          # Show current SDK version
./scripts/upgrade-expo.sh 55       # Upgrade to SDK 55
```

